# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

_MAKE_MOSAIC_SUBARRAY_ - Create mosaic of the four subarrays

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _MAKE_MOSAIC_SUBARRAY_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive takes all the aligned sub-scan frames from each
sub-array and mosaics them into a single output image. Its use is
optional but it helps speed up _MAKE_MOSAIC_FRAME_.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

Assumes the _ALIGN_ARRAYS_ primitive has been run on the input images.

=head1 ALGORITHMS

Uses CCDPACK MAKEMOS. 

=head1 FILE SUFFIX

Creates a single output image with a suffix of '_arr'.

